A BILL TO BE ENTITLED
AN ACT
1 To repeal an Act creating the Lower Chattahoochee Regional Airport Authority, approved
2 May 5, 2006 (Ga. L. 2006, p. 4422), as amended, particularly by an Act approved May 28,
3 2010 (Ga. L. 2010, p. 3570) and an Act approved April 11, 2012 (Ga. L. 2012, p. 5050); to
4 provide for the assets and liabilities thereof; to repeal conflicting laws; and for other
5 purposes.
6 BE IT ENACTED BY THE GENERAL ASSEMBLY OF GEORGIA:
7 SECTION 1.
8 An Act creating the Lower Chattahoochee Regional Airport Authority, approved May 5,
9 2006 (Ga. L. 2006, p. 4422), as amended, particularly by an Act approved May 28, 2010 (Ga.
10 L. 2010, p. 3570) and an Act approved April 11, 2012 (Ga. L. 2012, p. 5050), is hereby
11 repealed in its entirety.
12 SECTION 2.
13 Any and all assets of the Lower Chattahoochee Regional Airport Authority shall devolve
14 automatically and without further action to Randolph County, Georgia. The Board of
15 Commissioners of Randolph County, Georgia, is authorized to execute any deeds or
